OL,3,CCharities urge equal access at polling
OL,4,Cstations - what must they provide?
OL,6,FBy James Gray, ITV News Producer
OL,8,FCharities have urged polling stations
OL,9,Faround the United Kingdom to ensure
OL,10,Fthey do everything in their power to
OL,11,Fmake sure voting in the General
OL,12,FElection is "as accessible as
OL,13,Fpossible".
OL,15,FThe disability equality charity Scope
OL,16,Ftold ITV News that disabled voters can
OL,17,Fface a range of challenges when going
OL,18,Fto cast their ballot, including a lack
OL,19,Fof accessible parking or voting booths.
