OL,3,CCharities urge equal access at polling
OL,4,Cstations - what must they provide?
OL,6,FIt comes after the Royal National
OL,7,FInstitute of Blind People (RNIB)
OL,8,Fcalled it a "scandal" that blind and
OL,9,Fpartially sighted people are still
OL,10,Fhaving to share their ballot, despite
OL,11,Fthe right to vote in secret being
OL,12,Fbrought into British law more than 150
OL,13,Fyears ago.
OL,15,FITV News explains what provisions
OL,16,Fpolling stations must provide to
OL,17,Fensure equal access.
OL,19,F'You want to be independent'
