OL,3,CCharities urge equal access at polling
OL,4,Cstations - what must they provide?
OL,6,FSpeaking on ITV's Lorraine, blind
OL,7,Fcampaigner Lucy Edwards explained the
OL,8,Fchallenges faced by blind or partially
OL,9,Fsighted voters - many of whom have to
OL,10,Fbe accompanied into a voting booth.
OL,12,FShe said she often feels a "little bit
OL,13,Fjudged" when she casts her ballot,
OL,14,Fadding all she wants is to be able to
OL,15,F"vote in secret".
