OL,3,CCharities urge equal access at polling
OL,4,Cstations - what must they provide?
OL,6,FThe Electoral Commission has
OL,7,Fpreviously called on politicians to
OL,8,F"give disabled people more ways to
OL,9,Fvote", while the Equality Act 2010
OL,10,Fstates that returning officers at
OL,11,Fpolling stations must anticipate the
OL,12,Fneeds of disabled voters and make
OL,13,Freasonable adjustments to remove
OL,14,Fsignificant disadvantages for them.
